{"tid":1132324,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"（估歌手）IT男為追求音樂夢放棄過百萬年薪","createTime":"2019-04-30T08:24:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-30T10:46:45.000Z","uid":122522,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f1cde81381be50829814581744b8c0a086c9fb97","tid":1132324,"uid":122522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T08:24:13.000Z","msg":"老實講佢唱功算係新人算係中上（雖然都唔算新），點解香港冇咩人留意，聽佢個訪問自信爆棚，睇得出佢好想導正香港樂壇同藝術，香港再多kpop系、娘炮真係冇人再聽廣東歌！肯放棄高薪玩音樂呢個決定已經夠pop!<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2682111/org/361b247c6d10b7dcad997329b4e27cfe.jpg/4Qpc79BjOTmCU0hZBtaKAYI5q870BF9Ze1g0tHtYNLQ\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2682111%2Forg%2F361b247c6d10b7dcad997329b4e27cfe.jpg%2F4Qpc79BjOTmCU0hZBtaKAYI5q870BF9Ze1g0tHtYNLQ&h=25c68ddb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2682109/org/68092aff7b70af12c2b9a810ec65104f.jpg/nZEtHA-gr1MGc1nkJmhLktCnuvmmjk-4_yKXlP8il5Q\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2682109%2Forg%2F68092aff7b70af12c2b9a810ec65104f.jpg%2FnZEtHA-gr1MGc1nkJmhLktCnuvmmjk-4_yKXlP8il5Q&h=4855c7aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2682100/org/b595c8ac730102071cc39ea10be4cbbd.jpg/bpu-nW9_IClwBAsz-QmPClScegBozkU7ckH5qHJB-ag\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2682100%2Forg%2Fb595c8ac730102071cc39ea10be4cbbd.jpg%2Fbpu-nW9_IClwBAsz-QmPClScegBozkU7ckH5qHJB-ag&h=131c2f1f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n曾獲陳奕迅加持 藍調歌手易容Busking：觀眾對素人係寬容啲<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/演唱現場/318334/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E6%BC%94%E5%94%B1%E7%8F%BE%E5%A0%B4%2F318334%2F&d=jZUVzsr%2BlXwf2hbAbvJm1f%2FZYLwdGiEzwb2OZuYF8yg%3D&h=f1db87a0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/演唱現場/318334/</a><br />\n<br />\n其實符致逸由2001年已開始擔任作曲工作，後來更為了<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">追求音樂夢而放棄了高薪厚職的科技工作</span></span>。<span style=\"color: red;\">曾為陳奕迅《一切還好》、《我們都寂寞》、《路&hellip;一直都在》、鄭秀文《我就是愛你不害怕》等大熱作品作曲</span>，亦獲提名台灣《第26屆金曲獎》的「最佳新人獎」。<br />\n在香港出道不知不覺已來到第五個年頭，卻是<span style=\"color: red;\">紅歌不紅人</span>，大家在麥記買早餐時大概也會聽過「Flying By~是我的寂寞神態~」又或是近期「若是自己也會心死   ~實在值得我被放棄~」，《靈魂獨舞》及新歌《值得放棄》兩首作品自然是琅琅上口，但大家又會否願意多花時間留意這位有心有才華的音樂人？"},{"pid":"18b4012a5dfa770b5f924777683240355b20dacc","tid":1132324,"uid":186087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T10:43:41.000Z","msg":"it 狗, 唔做都唔會可惜"},{"pid":"e80e192c7b0c5626777d9be7c464d99a1eab2cfd","tid":1132324,"uid":5292,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T10:46:45.000Z","msg":"唔覺得佢做主持做得好<br />\n但覺得佢唱歌唔錯幾好聽<br />\n曲風都順耳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}